making an flask project
command: pip install flask

virtual environment:-
command: python venv <name of virtual environment>

activating virtual environment:
command: source virt/scripts/activate

starting the server:
commands:	1. export FLASK_DEBUG=True
			2. export FLASK_APP=main.py
			3. flask run

Follow the following steps to make version control

commands:
1. git config --global user.name "Ajay Kumar"
2. git config --global user.email "ajaykumarmohapatra871c@gmail.com"
3. git config --global push.default matching
4. git config --global alias.co checkout
5. git init